{"type": "article", "id": 7264, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考。", "date": "2015-03-11T08:51:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2285, "name": "时钟"}, {"id": 3149, "name": "灯具"}, {"id": 1409, "name": "厨房"}, {"id": 1242, "name": "服装"}], "category": 17, "column": null, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 81, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605210942iPvpCJLXk7eEKz08.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>\r\n\tNew Spring 2015 Collection of Areaware\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t美国设计品牌 Areaware 发布了他们的 2015 春季系列产品。这组产品包括冰箱贴，开瓶器，手环状酒杯，拼图，扑克牌，别针和案板等。 Areaware 延续简约时尚的设计风格，同时这一季主打五彩缤纷的颜色，并且采用了更多样的材料，如瓷器，玻璃，石头甚至电线等。<a href=\"http://www.areaware.com\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看并购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210930NcP6eyVatoQlOgJ7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060521093171ixAmYbyok3dPRX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052109316kSsdQ4NpWMbqChj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210932JDanXNo7UfCh4wPT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060521093246WCmyNU89Je1vbi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tTensegrity Space frame Lights by Michal Maciej Bartosik\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\tMichal Maciej Bartosik 推出的这款灯每一小节都由四根灯杆制成，其几何形状是立方形结构的派生。别看这个架子看起来很简单，其中却包含着严谨的科学知识。这种结构被称为 “Kenneth Snelson” 结构，来源于美国艺术家 Kenneth Snelson，他穷尽一生的时间做着同样一件事情，就是寻找方法把独立部件通过空间相互链接在一起，成为新的艺术品。感兴趣的话，你可以<a href=\"http://kennethsnelson.net/\" target=\"_blank\">点进这里</a>，看看他曾经做的各种精巧的结构作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210933MfeTUjy7mA5nhQD2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70520833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052109338Q3Pl9hcUXez5tFb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210934vc1SiTRFEXp5Ce3z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.08\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210934CHMDcRQFp97zaguO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.44\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210935wKkTujdAfSVIiUCZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tOver The Years by Eggpicnic\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t这是 Eggpicnic 推出的一款时钟，采用城市拆迁时的废弃建材制造。他们认为，建筑是城市的灵魂，而废弃建筑物材料中包含着城市的灵魂，用这些材料制作时钟，有着凝固时间的隐喻。这个时钟分三层，最下面一层底盘采用的是拆迁剩下的红砖，将红砖打碎成粉，与生物树脂结合制成。而上面的两层分别代表时针和分针的转盘，均由竹木制成。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052109359q0LyQeaIUhVT2ps.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210936ZozpBkr2QVFeD8OP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210937DGnwMx5dQuK6XhLb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210937pOgP5SYMDoE0Jnbw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210938mWLjTqJChNpIDkQf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tAquarium Kitchen Island by Robert Kolenik\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t荷兰设计师 Robert Kolenik 推出的这款厨房设计把厨房和水族馆结合在了一起，这个呈 “ L” 形状的水族箱上面铺设了一层白色的桌台，设置灶台，洗碗池等基本设施，同时水箱的多余空间被用作了收纳柜。而且顶部的桌台可以通过一个桌面按钮自由升降。这是<a href=\"http://www.kolenik.com/\" target=\"_blank\">他们的官网</a>，可以提供预订服务。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210938xITMuFBLn3ylm9Oj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48240741\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210939Y6B2bOXIQfz40rxs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210939gMlzpqoV6G5cL9rZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.45\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tMathematical Patterns by Junya Watanabe\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t日本服装设计师 Junya Watanabe 在巴黎时装周上展示了其品牌 2015 秋冬系列，这个由川保久玲一手捧红的设计师如今越来越前卫了，这次他让模特们把一堆立体的几何形状穿在了身上。这些立体的几何形状大多是自然界常见的数学形状，比如钻石样式。有的看起来酷酷的，有的看起来模特像是把一个纸灯笼套在了头上。这里没有链接，因为你肯定只是看看日本人的奇思妙想，肯定不会下单买的。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052109409vjhXwHJmx7qoUbC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.31623932\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210940ZyGiHDmjuoxaLT5W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.43589744\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210941HqeZ2jsuJ70d9Pt3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.46153846\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210941hNlvxo2bqUzgkXCY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.51709402\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210942rtoTcavX4pwyP2zB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.44444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}